    "description": "Dear Jos√©, you were funny, bright, warm, and so smart. I remember one day you spoke about ‚Äòus Africans‚Äô and I said, Jos√©, do you think of yourself as African? And you laughed and said, yes, I‚Äôm from the Canaries, I‚Äôm from Africa. It was a joy to work with you, it felt more like being in school together than being in a serious institution. So much love, Florence",
